17. How is the trailer hitches and towing accessories market affected by the fluctuating prices of raw materials?
The market is affected by the volatility in raw material prices, which directly impacts the manufacturing cost and pricing of towing accessories.

18. What are the factors influencing the purchasing decisions of consumers in the trailer hitches and towing accessories market?
Factors such as brand reputation, product quality, price, and warranty offerings influence the purchasing decisions of consumers in the market.

19. How are sustainability initiatives impacting the trailer hitches and towing accessories market?
